{"PERK":[{"def":"To make trim or smart; to straighten up; to erect; to make a jaunty or saucy display of; as, to perk the ears; to perk up one's head.","pos":""}],"PERKIN":[{"def":"A kind of weak perry.","pos":""}],"PERKINISM":[{"def":"A remedial treatment, by drawing the pointed extremities of two rods, each of a different metal, over the affected part; tractoration, -- first employed by Dr.","pos":""}],"PERKY":[{"def":"Perk; pert; jaunty; trim.","pos":""}]}